                    <h2>Amphibians</h2>
                    <p>It is common to observe large Bullfrogs in the wetland prairie, sunning themselves on the rocks.</p>
                    <p>Photos of reptiles and amphibians found at the Park courtesy of A.B. Sheldon and the Wisconsin DNR.
